var book = {
	"name": "1 Peter",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Peter, an apostle of Jesus Christ,To those who are elect exiles of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30359A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30359A\"></sup>the Dispersion in Pontus, Galatia, Cappadocia, Asia, and Bithynia,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30360B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30360B\"></sup>the foreknowledge of God the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30360C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30360C\"></sup>in the sanctification of the Spirit, for obedience to Jesus Christ and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30360D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30360D\"></sup>for sprinkling with his blood:May <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30360E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30360E\"></sup>grace and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30360F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30360F\"></sup>peace be multiplied to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30361G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30361G\"></sup>Blessed be the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30361H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30361H\"></sup>According to his great mercy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30361I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30361I\"></sup>he has caused us to be born again to a living hope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30361J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30361J\"></sup>through the resurrection of Jesus Christ from the dead,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30362K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30362K\"></sup>an inheritance that is imperishable, undefiled, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30362L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30362L\"></sup>unfading, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30362M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30362M\"></sup>kept in heaven for you,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>who by God's power are being guarded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30363N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30363N\"></sup>through faith for a salvation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30363O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30363O\"></sup>ready to be revealed in the last time.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In this you rejoice, though now for a little while, if necessary, you have been grieved by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30364P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30364P\"></sup>various trials,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30365Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30365Q\"></sup>the tested genuineness of your faith—more precious than gold that perishes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30365R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30365R\"></sup>though it is tested by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30365S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30365S\"></sup>fire—may be found to result in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30365T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30365T\"></sup>praise and glory and honor at the revelation of Jesus Christ.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30366U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30366U\"></sup>Though you have not seen him, you love him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30366V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30366V\"></sup>Though you do not now see him, you believe in him and rejoice with joy that is inexpressible and filled with glory,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>obtaining <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30367W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30367W\"></sup>the outcome of your faith, the salvation of your souls.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Concerning this salvation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30368X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30368X\"></sup>the prophets who prophesied about the grace that was to be yours searched and inquired carefully,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>inquiring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30369Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30369Y\"></sup>what person or time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30369Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30369Z\"></sup>the Spirit of Christ in them was indicating <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30369AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30369AA\"></sup>when he predicted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30369AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30369AB\"></sup>the sufferings of Christ and the subsequent glories.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30370AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30370AC\"></sup>It was revealed to them that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30370AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30370AD\"></sup>they were serving not themselves but you, in the things that have now been announced to you through those who preached the good news to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30370AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30370AE\"></sup>by the Holy Spirit sent from heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30370AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30370AF\"></sup>things into which angels long to look.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30371AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30371AG\"></sup>preparing your minds for action, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30371AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30371AH\"></sup>being sober-minded, set your hope fully on the grace that will be brought to you at the revelation of Jesus Christ.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As obedient children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30372AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30372AI\"></sup>do not be conformed to the passions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30372AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30372AJ\"></sup>of your former ignorance,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30373AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30373AK\"></sup>as he who called you is holy, you also be holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30373AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30373AL\"></sup>in all your conduct,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>since it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30374AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30374AM\"></sup>“You shall be holy, for I am holy.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30375AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30375AN\"></sup>call on him as Father who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30375AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30375AO\"></sup>judges <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30375AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30375AP\"></sup>impartially according to each one's deeds, conduct yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30375AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30375AQ\"></sup>with fear throughout the time of your exile,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>knowing that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30376AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30376AR\"></sup>were ransomed from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30376AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30376AS\"></sup>the futile ways inherited from your forefathers, not with perishable things such as silver or gold,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30377AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30377AT\"></sup>with the precious blood of Christ, like that of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30377AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30377AU\"></sup>a lamb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30377AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30377AV\"></sup>without blemish or spot.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He was foreknown before the foundation of the world but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30378AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30378AW\"></sup>was made manifest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30378AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30378AX\"></sup>in the last times for the sake of you",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30379AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30379AY\"></sup>who through him are believers in God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30379AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30379AZ\"></sup>who raised him from the dead and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30379BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30379BA\"></sup>gave him glory, so that your faith and hope are in God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Having purified your souls by your obedience to the truth for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30380BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30380BB\"></sup>a sincere brotherly love, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30380BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30380BC\"></sup>love one another earnestly from a pure heart,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30381BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30381BD\"></sup>since you have been born again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30381BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30381BE\"></sup>not of perishable seed but of imperishable, through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30381BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30381BF\"></sup>the living and abiding word of God;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30382BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30382BG\"></sup>“All flesh is like grassand all its glory like the flower of grass.The grass withers,and the flower falls,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30383BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30383BH\"></sup>but the word of the Lord remains forever.”And this word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30383BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30383BI\"></sup>is the good news that was preached to you."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30384A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30384A\"></sup>So put away all malice and all deceit and hypocrisy and envy and all slander.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30385B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30385B\"></sup>Like newborn infants, long for the pure spiritual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30385C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30385C\"></sup>milk, that by it you may grow up into salvation—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>if indeed you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30386D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30386D\"></sup>tasted that the Lord is good.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As you come to him, a living stone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30387E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30387E\"></sup>rejected by men but in the sight of God chosen and precious,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30388F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30388F\"></sup>you yourselves like living stones are being built up as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30388G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30388G\"></sup>a spiritual house, to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30388H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30388H\"></sup>a holy priesthood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30388I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30388I\"></sup>to offer spiritual sacrifices <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30388J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30388J\"></sup>acceptable to God through Jesus Christ.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For it stands in Scripture:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30389K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30389K\"></sup>“Behold, I am laying in Zion a stone,a cornerstone chosen and precious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30389L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30389L\"></sup>and whoever believes in him will not be put to shame.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So the honor is for you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30390M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30390M\"></sup>believe, but for those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30390N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30390N\"></sup>do not believe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30390O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30390O\"></sup>“The stone that the builders rejectedhas become the cornerstone,”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30391P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30391P\"></sup>“A stone of stumbling,and a rock of offense.”They stumble because they disobey the word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30391Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30391Q\"></sup>as they were destined to do.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392R\"></sup>a chosen race, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392S\"></sup>a royal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392T\"></sup>priesthood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392U\"></sup>a holy nation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392V\"></sup>a people for his own possession, that you may proclaim the excellencies of him who called you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392W\"></sup>out of darkness into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30392X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30392X\"></sup>his marvelous light.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30393Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30393Y\"></sup>Once you were not a people, but now you are God's people; once you had not received mercy, but now you have received mercy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Beloved, I urge you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30394Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30394Z\"></sup>as sojourners and exiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30394AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30394AA\"></sup>to abstain from the passions of the flesh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30394AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30394AB\"></sup>which wage war against your soul.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30395AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30395AC\"></sup>Keep your conduct among the Gentiles honorable, so that when they speak against you as evildoers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30395AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30395AD\"></sup>they may see your good deeds and glorify God on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30395AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30395AE\"></sup>the day of visitation.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30396AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30396AF\"></sup>Be subject for the Lord's sake to every human institution, whether it be to the emperor as supreme,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>or to governors as sent by him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30397AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30397AG\"></sup>to punish those who do evil and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30397AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30397AH\"></sup>to praise those who do good.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this is the will of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30398AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30398AI\"></sup>that by doing good you should put to silence the ignorance of foolish people.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30399AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30399AJ\"></sup>Live as people who are free, not using your freedom as a cover-up for evil, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30399AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30399AK\"></sup>living as servants of God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30400AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30400AL\"></sup>Honor everyone. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30400AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30400AM\"></sup>Love the brotherhood. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30400AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30400AN\"></sup>Fear God. Honor the emperor.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30401AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30401AO\"></sup>Servants, be subject to your masters with all respect, not only to the good and gentle but also to the unjust.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For this is a gracious thing, when, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30402AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30402AP\"></sup>mindful of God, one endures sorrows while suffering unjustly.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For what credit is it if, when you sin and are beaten for it, you endure? But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30403AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30403AQ\"></sup>if when you do good and suffer for it you endure, this is a gracious thing in the sight of God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30404AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30404AR\"></sup>to this you have been called, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30404AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30404AS\"></sup>because Christ also suffered for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30404AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30404AT\"></sup>leaving you an example, so that you might follow in his steps.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30405AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30405AU\"></sup>He committed no sin, neither was deceit found in his mouth.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30406AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30406AV\"></sup>When he was reviled, he did not revile in return; when he suffered, he did not threaten, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30406AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30406AW\"></sup>but continued entrusting himself to him who judges justly.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30407AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30407AX\"></sup>He himself bore our sins in his body on the tree, that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30407AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30407AY\"></sup>might die to sin and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30407AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30407AZ\"></sup>live to righteousness. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30407BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30407BA\"></sup>By his wounds you have been healed.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30408BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30408BB\"></sup>you were straying like sheep, but have now returned to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30408BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30408BC\"></sup>the Shepherd and Overseer of your souls."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Likewise, wives, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30409A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30409A\"></sup>be subject to your own husbands, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30409B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30409B\"></sup>even if some do not obey the word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30409C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30409C\"></sup>they may be won without a word by the conduct of their wives,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>when they see your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30410D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30410D\"></sup>respectful and pure conduct.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30411E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30411E\"></sup>Do not let your adorning be external—the braiding of hair and the putting on of gold jewelry, or the clothing you wear—",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but let your adorning be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30412F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30412F\"></sup>the hidden person of the heart with the imperishable beauty of a gentle and quiet spirit, which in God's sight is very precious.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For this is how the holy women who hoped in God used to adorn themselves, by submitting to their own husbands,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>as Sarah obeyed Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30414G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30414G\"></sup>calling him lord. And you are her children, if you do good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30414H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30414H\"></sup>do not fear anything that is frightening.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Likewise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30415I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30415I\"></sup>husbands, live with your wives in an understanding way, showing honor to the woman as the weaker <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30415J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30415J\"></sup>vessel, since they are heirs with you of the grace of life, so that your prayers may not be hindered.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Finally, all of you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30416K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30416K\"></sup>have unity of mind, sympathy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30416L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30416L\"></sup>brotherly love, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30416M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30416M\"></sup>a tender heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30416N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30416N\"></sup>a humble mind.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30417O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30417O\"></sup>Do not repay evil for evil or reviling for reviling, but on the contrary, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30417P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30417P\"></sup>bless, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30417Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30417Q\"></sup>to this you were called, that you may obtain a blessing.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30418R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30418R\"></sup>“Whoever desires to love lifeand see good days,let him keep his tongue from eviland his lips from speaking deceit;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>let him turn away from evil and do good;let him seek peace and pursue it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the eyes of the Lord are on the righteous,and his ears are open to their prayer.But the face of the Lord is against those who do evil.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30421S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30421S\"></sup>who is there to harm you if you are zealous for what is good?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30422T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30422T\"></sup>But even if you should suffer for righteousness' sake, you will be blessed. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30422U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30422U\"></sup>Have no fear of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30422V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30422V\"></sup>nor be troubled,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30423W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30423W\"></sup>in your hearts honor Christ the Lord as holy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30423X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30423X\"></sup>always being prepared to make a defense to anyone who asks you for a reason for the hope that is in you; yet do it with gentleness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30423Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30423Y\"></sup>respect,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30424Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30424Z\"></sup>having a good conscience, so that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30424AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30424AA\"></sup>when you are slandered, those who revile your good behavior in Christ may be put to shame.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30425AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30425AB\"></sup>it is better to suffer for doing good, if that should be God's will, than for doing evil.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For Christ also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30426AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30426AC\"></sup>suffered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30426AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30426AD\"></sup>once for sins, the righteous for the unrighteous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30426AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30426AE\"></sup>that he might bring us to God, being put to death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30426AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30426AF\"></sup>in the flesh but made alive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30426AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30426AG\"></sup>in the spirit,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>in which he went and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30427AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30427AH\"></sup>proclaimed to the spirits in prison,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>because they formerly did not obey, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30428AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30428AI\"></sup>when God's patience waited in the days of Noah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30428AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30428AJ\"></sup>while the ark was being prepared, in which a few, that is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30428AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30428AK\"></sup>eight persons, were brought safely through water.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Baptism, which corresponds to this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30429AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30429AL\"></sup>now saves you, not as a removal of dirt from the body but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30429AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30429AM\"></sup>as an appeal to God for a good conscience, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30429AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30429AN\"></sup>through the resurrection of Jesus Christ,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>who has gone into heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30430AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30430AO\"></sup>is at the right hand of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30430AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30430AP\"></sup>with angels, authorities, and powers having been subjected to him."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Since therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30431A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30431A\"></sup>Christ suffered in the flesh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30431B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30431B\"></sup>arm yourselves with the same way of thinking, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30431C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30431C\"></sup>whoever has suffered in the flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30431D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30431D\"></sup>has ceased from sin,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30432E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30432E\"></sup>so as to live for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30432F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30432F\"></sup>the rest of the time in the flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30432G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30432G\"></sup>no longer for human passions but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30432H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30432H\"></sup>for the will of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the time that is past <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30433I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30433I\"></sup>suffices <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30433J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30433J\"></sup>for doing what the Gentiles want to do, living in sensuality, passions, drunkenness, orgies, drinking parties, and lawless idolatry.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>With respect to this they are surprised when you do not join them in the same flood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30434K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30434K\"></sup>debauchery, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30434L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30434L\"></sup>they malign you;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>but they will give account to him who is ready <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30435M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30435M\"></sup>to judge the living and the dead.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For this is why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30436N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30436N\"></sup>the gospel was preached even to those who are dead, that though judged in the flesh the way people are, they might live in the spirit the way God does.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30437O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30437O\"></sup>The end of all things is at hand; therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30437P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30437P\"></sup>be self-controlled and sober-minded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30437Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30437Q\"></sup>for the sake of your prayers.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Above all, keep loving one another earnestly, since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30438R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30438R\"></sup>love covers a multitude of sins.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30439S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30439S\"></sup>Show hospitality to one another without grumbling.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30440T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30440T\"></sup>As each has received a gift, use it to serve one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30440U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30440U\"></sup>as good stewards of God's varied grace:",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>whoever speaks, as one who speaks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30441V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30441V\"></sup>oracles of God; whoever serves, as one who serves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30441W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30441W\"></sup>by the strength that God supplies—in order that in everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30441X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30441X\"></sup>God may be glorified through Jesus Christ. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30441Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30441Y\"></sup>To him belong glory and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30441Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30441Z\"></sup>dominion forever and ever. Amen.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Beloved, do not be surprised at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30442AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30442AA\"></sup>the fiery trial when it comes upon you to test you, as though something strange were happening to you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But rejoice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30443AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30443AB\"></sup>insofar as you share Christ's sufferings, that you may also rejoice and be glad <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30443AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30443AC\"></sup>when his glory is revealed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30444AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30444AD\"></sup>If you are insulted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30444AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30444AE\"></sup>for the name of Christ, you are blessed, because the Spirit of glory and of God rests upon you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30445AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30445AF\"></sup>let none of you suffer as a murderer or a thief or an evildoer or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30445AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30445AG\"></sup>as a meddler.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30446AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30446AH\"></sup>if anyone suffers as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30446AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30446AI\"></sup>Christian, let him not be ashamed, but let him glorify God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30446AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30446AJ\"></sup>in that name.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For it is time for judgment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30447AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30447AK\"></sup>to begin at the household of God; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30447AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30447AL\"></sup>if it begins with us, what will be the outcome for those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30447AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30447AM\"></sup>do not obey the gospel of God?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30448AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30448AN\"></sup>“If the righteous is scarcely saved,what will become of the ungodly and the sinner?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore let those who suffer according to God's will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30449AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30449AO\"></sup>entrust their souls to a faithful Creator while doing good."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>So I exhort the elders among you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30450A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30450A\"></sup>as a fellow elder and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30450B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30450B\"></sup>a witness of the sufferings of Christ, as well as a partaker in the glory that is going to be revealed:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30451C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30451C\"></sup>shepherd the flock of God that is among you, exercising oversight, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30451D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30451D\"></sup>not under compulsion, but willingly, as God would have you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30451E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30451E\"></sup>not for shameful gain, but eagerly;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30452F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30452F\"></sup>domineering over those in your charge, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30452G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30452G\"></sup>being examples to the flock.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30453H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30453H\"></sup>the chief Shepherd appears, you will receive the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30453I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30453I\"></sup>unfading <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30453J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30453J\"></sup>crown of glory.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Likewise, you who are younger, be subject to the elders. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30454K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30454K\"></sup>Clothe yourselves, all of you, with humility toward one another, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30454L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30454L\"></sup>“God opposes the proud but gives grace to the humble.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30455M\"></sup>Humble yourselves, therefore, under the mighty hand of God so that at the proper time he may exalt you,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30456N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30456N\"></sup>casting all your anxieties on him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30456O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30456O\"></sup>he cares for you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30457P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30457P\"></sup>Be sober-minded; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30457Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30457Q\"></sup>be watchful. Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30457R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30457R\"></sup>adversary the devil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30457S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30457S\"></sup>prowls around <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30457T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30457T\"></sup>like a roaring lion, seeking someone to devour.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30458U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30458U\"></sup>Resist him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30458V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30458V\"></sup>firm in your faith, knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30458W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30458W\"></sup>the same kinds of suffering are being experienced by your brotherhood throughout the world.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30459X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30459X\"></sup>after you have suffered a little while, the God of all grace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30459Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30459Y\"></sup>who has called you to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30459Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30459Z\"></sup>eternal glory in Christ, will himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30459AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30459AA\"></sup>restore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30459AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30459AB\"></sup>confirm, strengthen, and establish you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30460AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30460AC\"></sup>To him be the dominion forever and ever. Amen.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30461AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30461AD\"></sup>Silvanus, a faithful brother as I regard him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30461AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30461AE\"></sup>I have written briefly to you, exhorting and declaring that this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30461AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30461AF\"></sup>the true grace of God. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30461AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30461AG\"></sup>Stand firm in it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She who is at Babylon, who is likewise chosen, sends you greetings, and so does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30462AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30462AH\"></sup>Mark, my son.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30463AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30463AI\"></sup>Greet one another with the kiss of love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30463AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30463AJ\"></sup>Peace to all of you who are in Christ."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;